logFile leap.log
#
# ----- leaprc for loading ff15ipq fluorinated, aromatic amino acid residues
#       D.T. Yang, A.M Gronenborn, L.T. Chong, Development and Validation
#       of Fluorinated, Aromatic Amino Acid Parameters for Use with the
#       AMBER ff15ipq Protein Force Field
#       J. Phys. Chem. A, 126, 14, 2286-2297 (2022).
#
# This file contains IPolQ optimized parameters for fluorinated amino acids:
#
# F4F:   4(para)-fluoro-phenylalanine
# FTF:   4(para)-trifluoromethyl-phenylalanine
# Y3F:   3(meta)-fluoro-tyrosine
# YDF:   3,5(meta)-difluro-tyrosine
# W4F:   4-fluoro-tryptophan
# W5F:   5-fluoro-tryptophan
# W6F:   6-fluoro-tryptophan
# W7F:   7-fluoro-tryptophan
#
# To use these residues, load this file into leap, after the Amber-FF, e.g.:
#
# > source leaprc.protein.ff15ipq
# > source leaprc.fluorine.ff15ipq
#
#   Load the fluorinated amino acid parameter set.
#
loadamberparams frcmod.ff15ipq-19F
#
#   Load the fluorinated amino acid libraries.
#
# load individual residues
loadoff ff15ipq-19F.lib
